devdoc.author: Thomas for Alyra Certifaction
devdoc.details: Implements donations in exchange for ERC721 tokens.

Approval(address,address,uint256).details: Emitted when `owner` enables `approved` to manage the `tokenId` token.

ApprovalForAll(address,address,bool).details: Emitted when `owner` enables or disables (`approved`) `operator` to manage all of its assets.

NewDonation(address,uint256,uint256,uint.details: Event emitted when a new donation is made

Transfer(address,address,uint256).details: Emitted when `tokenId` token is transferred from `from` to `to`.

constructor.details: Sets the name and symbol of the token

donate().details: Enables external accounts to make a donation and receive an ERC721 token

getContractBalance().details: Returns the balance of the contract

getDonationDetails(uint256).details: Returns the details of a specific donation

nbDonationsTotal().details: Returns the total number of donations made

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

setPrice(uint256).details: Allows the owner to set a new min donation price

supportsInterface(bytes4).details: Overrides supportsInterface to use multiple inheritance in contract

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

walletOfOwner(address).details: Returns a list of donation IDs for a given address

withdraw().details: Allows the owner to withdraw all funds from the contract

devdoc.title: Donate contract
